<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森看着窗外的雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>儿童中心今天在室内活动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面太湿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雨会把雪都融化掉的。” 莉琪伤心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“十二月不该下雨的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们，开心点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在是十二月，肯定还会下雪的。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要做一个让大家都开心的食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要做巧克力豆腐布丁！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有牛奶，对吗？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只有豆腐、可可粉、香蕉和糖。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比抱怨道：“豆腐？呃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比，你吃过豆腐吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么尝尝新的食物会很有趣的。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森看着桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么做呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“围上围裙，我教你们。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一定很难吃。” 波比皱着眉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比。” 雪莉老师看了波比一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好吃的，你就试试嘛。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢豆腐！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，你来开始吧。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“沥干一包豆腐。” 贾森念道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放进搅拌机。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么是沥干豆腐？” 莉琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是把水倒掉。” 贾森回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“加一根香蕉。” 莉琪念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“加可可粉。” 伊坦把可可粉放到搅拌机里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“加糖。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“搅拌。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可以让我按按钮吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>搅拌机发出轰轰声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一开始很吵，后来安静了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们该怎么办？” 波比问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“搅拌机是开着的，但是没有在搅拌！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布丁不动了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“关掉后用这个刮一刮。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师给他一把勺子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后再搅拌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比按照老师的话做了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他重新按按钮时，布丁转了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得可以了！” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“关掉搅拌机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人拿一个纸杯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把布丁倒进纸杯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要把布丁放进冰箱半个小时。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师把托盘放到冰箱里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们在体育馆里打篮球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快就到回家时间了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弗拉尼校长的头从门口伸进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冰箱里有贴着你们名字的东西。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的布丁！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家坐下来，各拿了一杯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。” 贾森边吃边说，“真好吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“闻起来很奇怪。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他闻了闻杯子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尝一尝嘛。” 贾森转了转眼睛说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好吃的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比尝了一口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不是巧克力布丁的味道吗！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为这就是巧克力布丁，傻瓜。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森对雪莉老师说：“谢谢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师笑了。“不用谢，贾森。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您让我尝豆腐。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“豆腐没那么难吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>